<%# booking_mailer/cancellation_notice.text.erb %>
Hi <%= @booking.guest_name %>,

Your booking session for The Anchorpoint Retreat has expired because payment was not completed within the required time.

----
Confirmation Number: <%= @booking.confirmation_number %>
Dates: <%= @booking.check_in.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %> – <%= @booking.check_out.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
Guests: <%= @booking.num_guests %>
Total: <%= number_to_currency(@booking.total_cents / 100.0) %>
----

Your dates have been released and are now available for others to book. If you'd still like to stay with us, please visit our website to start a new booking.

Visit: <%= root_url %>

If you have any questions or need assistance, reply to this email or contact us at hello@anchorpointretreat.com.

&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> The Anchorpoint Retreat
anchorpointretreat.com
